    public class CycEvaluateFunction
extends SublObjectSingleArgFunction<CycObject>
    Evaluate the evaluatable EXPRESSION and return the result. E.g., (CYC-EVALUATE '(#$IndexicalReferentFn #$Now-Indexical))

    nwinant
